                            <span className="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-400 to-purple-400">modern businesses.</span>
                        </h1>
                        <p className="text-lg text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
                            Generate GST invoices, manage inventory, and track payments seamlessly. Join thousands of businesses scaling with InvoicePro.
                        </p>

                        <FeaturesList />
                    </div>
                </div>

