                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" className="h-5 w-5 text-accent" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor"><path fillRule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm1-12a1 1 0 10-2 0v4a1 1 0 00.293.707l2.828 2.829a1 1 0 101.415-1.415L11 9.586V6z" clipRule="evenodd" /></svg>
                    Client History & Analytics
