                    <div className="absolute right-0 top-0 p-3 opacity-10 text-blue-500"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" className="h-12 w-12" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path strokeLinecap="round" strokeLinejoin="round" strokeWidth={2} d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2" /></svg></div>
                    <p className="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Invoice Count</p>
